Text: I can't get it patched somehow, i close REAPER, i apply patch, it says it's patched, and then i register. After that when i open up reaper it still says EVALUATION VERSION. On my laptop it's not like this, it just cracks it. Can someone help me please?

The patch works, just fill in the name, patch, register, that's it.

ANYONE WHO IS HAVING TROUBLE:
1) open keygen....
2) **CHANGE THE LICENSE TYPE TO SMALL BUSINESS YOU HAVE TO DO THIS FOR IT TO WORK**
3) choose operating system
4) click register
5) click Patch
6) Then select Reaper application from folder that opens then hit OK
7) your finished:) hope this helps everyone who has been having problems
**I forgot to mention...pick a nick name
